| caption1 = [[Ixtonton]] Stela 2 on display at the [[Museo Regional del Sureste de Petén]] in [[Dolores, El Petén|Dolores]], Guatemala{{sfn|Corzo|2005|p=781}}
| image2 = Maya stelae Aguateca Santiago.JPG
| width2 = 180
| alt2 = An upright stone slab with the front face flat and inscribed with two elaborately dressed figures facing each other, with a double column of hieroglyphs between them.
